This page is a portal for all of the characters in The Simpsons. Characters that are deceased permanently in the Simpsons universe have their names italicized. This page is under construction.

Note: This is incomplete.

Main Characters[]

The members of the Simpson family are the main focus of the show.

Major Characters[]

The few secondary characters that have been an important part of many episodes and have greatly influenced the history and identity of the show.
